import {
  Box,
  TextField,
  MenuItem,
  FormControl,
  Grid,
  Divider,
  Chip,
} from "@mui/material";
import { LoadingButton } from "@mui/lab";
import axios from "axios";
import { useState } from "react";

const days = [...Array(32).keys()];
days.shift();

const months = [...Array(13).keys()];
months.shift();

const years = [];

for (let i = 1900; i <= Date.Now().getFullYear(); i++) {
  years.push(i);
}

const Register = () => {
  const [inputValue, setInputValue] = useState({
    name: "",
    email: "",
    password: "",
    confirmPassword: "",
    sex: "",
    day: "",
    month: "",
    year: "",
    height: "",
    weight: "",
  });

  return (
    <Box
      component="div"
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        flexWrap: "wrap",
        maxWidth: 600,
        border: ".1px solid lightgray",
        borderRadius: ".3rem",
      }}
      ml="auto"
      mr="auto"
      p={4}
      gap={2}
    >
      <Box component="form">
        <Grid
          container
          spacing={2}
          sx={{ alignItems: "center", justifyContent: "center" }}
        >
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Divider light style={{ width: "100%" }} textAlign="center">
              <Chip label="Cont" size="small" />
            </Divider>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="text"
                label="Nume"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                name="name"
                onChange={(e) =>
                  setInputValue((prev) => ({
                    ...inputValue,
                    [e.target.name]: e.target.value,
                  }))
                }
                value={inputValue.name}
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="email"
                label="Email"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                name="email"
                onChange={(e) =>
                  setInputValue((prev) => ({
                    ...inputValue,
                    [e.target.name]: e.target.value,
                  }))
                }
                value={inputValue.email}
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="password"
                label="Parolă"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                name="password"
                onChange={(e) =>
                  setInputValue((prev) => ({
                    ...inputValue,
                    [e.target.name]: e.target.value,
                  }))
                }
                value={inputValue.password}
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="password"
                label="Confirmare parolă"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                name="confirmPassword"
                onChange={(e) =>
                  setInputValue((prev) => ({
                    ...inputValue,
                    [e.target.name]: e.target.value,
                  }))
                }
                value={inputValue.confirmPassword}
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Divider light style={{ width: "100%" }} textAlign="center">
              <Chip label="Fizic" size="small" />
            </Divider>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                label="Sex"
                variant="outlined"
                select
                value=""
                size="small"
              >
                <MenuItem value=""></MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="m">M</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="f">F</MenuItem>
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" select value="" label="Zi">
                {days.map((day, i) => (
                  <MenuItem key={i} value={day}>
                    {day}
                  </MenuItem>
                ))}
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" select value="" label="Luna">
                {months.map((month, i) => (
                  <MenuItem key={i} value={month}>
                    {month}
                  </MenuItem>
                ))}
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" label="An" select value="">
                {years.map((year, i) => (
                  <MenuItem key={i} value={year}>
                    {year}
                  </MenuItem>
                ))}
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" label="Înălțime (cm)"></TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" label="Greutate curentă (kg)"></TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
      <LoadingButton
        variant="contained"
        loadingPosition="center"
        sx={{
          fontSize: "1rem",
          alignSelf: "flex-start",
          textTransform: "capitalize",
          backgroundColor: "primary.main",
          "&:hover": { backgroundColor: "primary.dark" },
        }}
      >
        Înregistrare
      </LoadingButton>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
